<div class="docs-getstarted-page">
  <h1>Getting Started</h1>
  <p class="docs-getstarted-intro">Get SoftUI into your project in under a minute.</p>

  <div class="docs-getstarted-section">
    <h2>Install via package manager</h2>
<div class="docs-getstarted-code"><pre><code>npm install softui-css</code></pre></div>
<div class="docs-getstarted-code"><pre><code>yarn add softui-css</code></pre></div>
<div class="docs-getstarted-code"><pre><code>pnpm add softui-css</code></pre></div>
<div class="docs-getstarted-code"><pre><code>bun add softui-css</code></pre></div>
    <p>Then import in your HTML:</p>
<div class="docs-getstarted-code"><pre><code>&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="node_modules/softui-css/dist/softui.min.css"&gt;
&lt;script src="node_modules/softui-css/dist/softui.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre></div>
  </div>

  <div class="docs-getstarted-section">
    <h2>CDN</h2>
    <p>No build step needed. Add these two lines to your <code>&lt;head&gt;</code>:</p>
<div class="docs-getstarted-code"><pre><code>&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/softui-css/dist/softui.min.css"&gt;
&lt;script src="https://unpkg.com/softui-css/dist/softui.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code></pre></div>
  </div>

  <div class="docs-getstarted-section">
    <h2>Quick start</h2>
    <p>All components use the <code>sui-</code> prefix. Here's a minimal page:</p>
<div class="docs-getstarted-code"><pre><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html lang="en"&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
  &lt;meta charset="UTF-8"&gt;
  &lt;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"&gt;
  &lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/softui-css/dist/softui.min.css"&gt;
  &lt;script src="https://unpkg.com/softui-css/dist/softui.min.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
  &lt;button class="sui-btn sui-btn-primary"&gt;Click me&lt;/button&gt;

  &lt;div class="sui-card" style="padding: 24px; max-width: 360px; margin-top: 16px;"&gt;
    &lt;h3&gt;Hello SoftUI&lt;/h3&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;A neumorphic card with a soft raised shadow.&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre></div>
  </div>

  <div class="docs-getstarted-section">
    <h2>Dark mode</h2>
    <p>Add <code>data-theme="dark"</code> to the <code>&lt;html&gt;</code> element. All components adapt automatically.</p>
<div class="docs-getstarted-code"><pre><code>&lt;html data-theme="dark"&gt;</code></pre></div>
  </div>

  <div class="docs-getstarted-section">
    <h2>Customization</h2>
    <p>SoftUI is built on CSS custom properties. Override them to match your brand:</p>
<div class="docs-getstarted-code"><pre><code>:root {
  --sui-primary: #7C5CFC;
  --sui-radius: 12px;
  --sui-shadow-raised: 6px 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15),
                       -6px -6px 12px rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
}</code></pre></div>
  </div>

  <div class="docs-getstarted-section" style="text-align:center;padding-top:16px;">
